<!doctype html>
<html lang="sk">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title><%= title %> — Bytezone</title>
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    body {
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      max-width: 540px;
      margin: 6rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .code { font-size: 5rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0; color: #d0d7de; }
    h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem; }
    p { color: #666; }
    code {
      background: rgba(127,127,127,0.15);
      padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
    a { color: #0969da; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      .code { color: #30363d; }
      p { color: #999; }
      a { color: #58a6ff; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <p class="code">404</p>
  <h1>Stránka nenájdená</h1>
  <p>Adresa <code><%= url %></code> neexistuje alebo bola presunutá.</p>
  <p><a href="/">← Späť na úvod</a></p>
</body>
</html>
